title: King Tubby - A Declaration Of Dub
description:
King Tubby - A Declaration Of Dub



A man whose inspiration and creativity changed the course of the music business as we know it today.' The words of
 BBC DJ David Rodigan in a radio documentary refer to King Tubby, a producer who let his music do the talking.
 Disco, dance, rap, rave music and the whole remix culture all owe their origins to King Tubby, This classic 2 disc dub
 compilation showcases some of his best, including tracks "Free Africa", "Burial" and "Declaration Of Dub.
